[
  {
    "startTime": 14.52,
    "endTime": 16.74,
    "text": "Coffee is better than tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.44,
    "endTime": 19.1,
    "text": "That's an opinion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.1,
    "endTime": 22.28,
    "text": "It's not an argument in academic terms,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.28,
    "endTime": 23.48,
    "text": "although you might want"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.48,
    "endTime": 25.28,
    "text": "to argue with the opinion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.26,
    "endTime": 35.4,
    "text": "Now this is an academic argument:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.4,
    "endTime": 37.699,
    "text": "Statement one: Caffeine stimulates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.7,
    "endTime": 40.34,
    "text": "the brain and nervous system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.34,
    "endTime": 41.32,
    "text": "Statement two:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.32,
    "endTime": 44.42,
    "text": "Coffee contains more caffeine than tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.42,
    "endTime": 47.42,
    "text": "And statement three is the conclusion:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.42,
    "endTime": 49.18,
    "text": "Therefore coffee is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.18,
    "endTime": 52.66,
    "text": "more stimulating than tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.66,
    "endTime": 54.519,
    "text": "An argument is a collection"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.52,
    "endTime": 56.160000000000004,
    "text": "of statements which,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.16,
    "endTime": 58.318999999999996,
    "text": "when you consider them together,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.32,
    "endTime": 59.96,
    "text": "allows you to make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.96,
    "endTime": 62.813,
    "text": "another statement or a conclusion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.18,
    "endTime": 66.4,
    "text": "Making and evaluating arguments is one of the key functions of critical thinking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.8,
    "endTime": 70.88,
    "text": "We'll come back to this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.16,
    "endTime": 72.6,
    "text": "You've probably heard"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.6,
    "endTime": 75.38,
    "text": "this term 'critical thinking' before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.38,
    "endTime": 77.74,
    "text": "But what exactly does it mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.34,
    "endTime": 79.9,
    "text": "It's what you do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.9,
    "endTime": 82.66000000000001,
    "text": "when you evaluate information"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.66,
    "endTime": 84.34,
    "text": "and make decisions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.34,
    "endTime": 86.9,
    "text": "And it's crucial if"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.9,
    "endTime": 88.24000000000001,
    "text": "you want to become"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.24,
    "endTime": 90.74,
    "text": "an independent thinker:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.74,
    "endTime": 93.44,
    "text": "if you want to think for yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.44,
    "endTime": 95.679,
    "text": "And if you want to get good grades."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.64,
    "endTime": 101.32000000000001,
    "text": "You can defend your opinions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.6,
    "endTime": 104.199,
    "text": "and evaluate theories,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.21,
    "endTime": 108.689,
    "text": "finding their weaknesses and strengths."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.689,
    "endTime": 112.52,
    "text": "So, it sounds like a good thing, doesn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.52,
    "endTime": 115.899,
    "text": "But how do you do it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.9,
    "endTime": 118.799,
    "text": "Back to our argument."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.799,
    "endTime": 120.38000000000001,
    "text": "If you're a critical thinker and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.38,
    "endTime": 121.619,
    "text": "someone tells you coffee"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.62,
    "endTime": 123.79,
    "text": "is more stimulating than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.79,
    "endTime": 125.71900000000001,
    "text": "tea, what do you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.719,
    "endTime": 128.78,
    "text": "First, examine their argument."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.78,
    "endTime": 131.38,
    "text": "Is there a logical connection between the statements?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.9,
    "endTime": 134.48000000000002,
    "text": "I think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.48,
    "endTime": 137.899,
    "text": "Then you'd examine their sources."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.9,
    "endTime": 140.32,
    "text": "Ask questions like these:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.32,
    "endTime": 141.9,
    "text": "whose work is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.9,
    "endTime": 143.52,
    "text": "When was it written?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.52,
    "endTime": 145.98000000000002,
    "text": "How was the research funded?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.98,
    "endTime": 149.72,
    "text": "What methods were used to find the evidence?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.72,
    "endTime": 151.46,
    "text": "Is it objective –"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.46,
    "endTime": 154.20000000000002,
    "text": "what's fact and what's opinion?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.2,
    "endTime": 156.695,
    "text": "What has been left out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.695,
    "endTime": 158.88,
    "text": "What other perspectives or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.88,
    "endTime": 160.74,
    "text": "points of view could there be?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.7,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Ask questions to analyse these sources,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "compare them with other sources,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 170.56,
    "text": "and synthesise your findings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.24,
    "endTime": 173.32000000000002,
    "text": "And it's important to try"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.32,
    "endTime": 177.26,
    "text": "to put your own biases to one side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.26,
    "endTime": 178.28,
    "text": "We all have them:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.28,
    "endTime": 181.54,
    "text": "\"I have to say I prefer coffee,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.54,
    "endTime": 183.62,
    "text": "so I'll look for evidence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.62,
    "endTime": 185.98000000000002,
    "text": "that supports my view.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.98,
    "endTime": 189.66,
    "text": "And look out for any assumptions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.66,
    "endTime": 192.48,
    "text": "\"Well, coffee's good for you, isn't it?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.5,
    "endTime": 201.4,
    "text": "And critical thinking can be applied to more than just reading,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 205.92,
    "text": "you can write critically too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.92,
    "endTime": 207.48,
    "text": "Phrases like these are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.48,
    "endTime": 209.7,
    "text": "a great way to introduce sources and evidence:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.4,
    "endTime": 213.5,
    "text": "'It can be argued that…'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.14,
    "endTime": 217.119,
    "text": "'There is evidence to suggest that…'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.46,
    "endTime": 223.64000000000001,
    "text": "'This supports the conclusion that…'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.1,
    "endTime": 225.56,
    "text": "So, go out,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.56,
    "endTime": 226.92000000000002,
    "text": "find out more about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.92,
    "endTime": 228.35899999999998,
    "text": "this huge topic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.36,
    "endTime": 231.34,
    "text": "and try it out for yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.34,
    "endTime": 234.34,
    "text": "Critical thinking is like a muscle:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.34,
    "endTime": 237.18,
    "text": "it gets stronger the more you work at it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.19,
    "endTime": 238.78,
    "text": "Of course, you'll need"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.78,
    "endTime": 241.78,
    "text": "a fully alert and stimulated mind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.78,
    "endTime": 244.39000000000001,
    "text": "in order to get down to work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.39,
    "endTime": 246.45899999999997,
    "text": "Which leaves one question:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.46,
    "endTime": 248.46,
    "text": "which is better:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.46,
    "endTime": 250.36,
    "text": "coffee or tea?"
  }
]